      - 'Probe All APIs' button ΓÇö sweep all routes
      - 'Probe All LLMs' button ΓÇö test each model individually
      - 'Probe ΓåÆ Diagnose ΓåÆ Heal' button ΓÇö full automated pipeline
      - Color-coded model status cards (green/red/yellow/grey)
      - Consensus diagnosis display with agreement/disagreement indicators
    
